name: Lil EGG Monsters by Karrie Ross

metadata.description:
These are Lil EGG Monsters digital collectables minted on my own ERC721A smart contract using niftykit-dropkit on the ethereum blockchain

They have a story some is explained on the tokens, some I leave up to your imagination but this is HALLOWEEN and anything is possible. Please enjoy the one you save, it will follow you forever each October.

I hope you like my creations, the base images were created with GAN and I hand embellished each one with color, scenes and words to further their mystery. Please review more of my art here: https://linktr.ee/karrieross on Twitter

------------- 
Ross's distinctive, metaphorical, whimsical narrative, thought-provoking, abstract pieces revolve around the central theme of energy. She believes that the potential to create one's own energy has the power to alter a person's experiences & life circumstances. Please let me know if you have questions http://www.karrieross.com
